<item>
            <title>[LU-1247] After recovery 7 of 16 OST were deactivated by MDS.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1247</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When recovering from failure, 7 of the 16 OSTs on the system were deactivated on the MDS.&lt;br/&gt;
The system was down for some hours. Then the fs was restarted (MDS rebooted), and after that, we saw:&lt;br/&gt;
snxs2n001 kernel: [ 4557.366336] LustreError: 22332:0:(lov_obd.c:1071:lov_clear_orphans()) error in orphan recovery on OST idx 11/16: rc = -22&lt;br/&gt;
snxs2n001 kernel: [ 4557.366343] LustreError: 22332:0:(mds_lov.c:880:__mds_lov_synchronize()) snxs2-OST000b_UUID failed at mds_lov_clear_orphans: -22&lt;br/&gt;
snxs2n001 kernel: [ 4557.366348] LustreError: 22332:0:(mds_lov.c:901:__mds_lov_synchronize()) snxs2-OST000b_UUID sync failed -22, deactivating&lt;br/&gt;
...&lt;br/&gt;
snxs2n004 kernel: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;343022.475923&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; LustreError: 11898:0:(filter.c:3653:filter_handle_precreate()) snxs2-OST000b: ignoring bogus orphan destroy request: obdid 4710212 last_id 4730465&lt;br/&gt;
snxs2n004 kernel: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;343022.522962&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Lustre: Skipped 5 previous similar messages&lt;/p&gt;</description>
